{"tid":1816464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你拜年之新春嘉年華係林奠政府送的國際戰線","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T13:24:44.000Z","uid":125506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3653e24a266ed44ab5ed6aed9b6ea702fd227baf","tid":1816464,"uid":125506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200108/s00002/1578423212835/%E6%96%B0%E6%98%A5%E5%8C%AF%E6%BC%94-%E6%97%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%80-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200108%2Fs00002%2F1578423212835%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2598%25A5%25E5%258C%25AF%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=acf8a204\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200108%2Fs00002%2F1578423212835%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2598%25A5%25E5%258C%25AF%25E6%25BC%2594-%25E6%2597%2585%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4&h=63c5f2f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200108/s00002/1578423212835/%E6%96%B0%E6%98%A5%E5%8C%AF%E6%BC%94-%E6%97%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%80-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%A5%E6%9C%83%E5%A0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n「若屆時有人高叫口號或唱歌等表達訴求，只要不影響他人，不會阻止，又稱警方表明不會主動進入會場巡邏。&hellip;<br />\n整個活動斥資4200萬元，比去年的花車巡遊開支多了800萬元&hellip;<br />\n警方不會主動進入會場巡邏，而嘉年華入口則不排除有安檢。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係和勇每次遊行都被打被圍捕、濫捕的情況下，無數傷亡，旅發局繼俾200萬整個無人上到的網站後又用4200萬公帑維穩 &ndash; 新春嘉年華，初一至四破紀錄請左26隊國際表演隊伍黎香港。旅發局大灑維穩費下，由1日花車變出4日嘉年華，目的就係要粉飾太平，話俾國外人聽，香港好和平，無被中共政治逼害，咁多隊外國團隊都平平安安，番去可以同國民講香港無事。咁樣好易令國際就會唔再關注香港，無人去制裁林奠政權同埋班黑警，獨立調查漸漸被淡忘。<br />\n<br />\n我！未敢忘記手足！ 我！未敢忘記所有被控、被打到頭破血流的手足。<br />\n<br />\n係近排，勇武多次俾黑警拉人搜屋，係時候由我地呢班和理非補上，俾勇武休息下。初一至四，大家收少幾封利是，訓少幾個鐘，食少幾件糕，魔法同GEAR 都唔好帶，俾班狗搜到(加上有安檢)。一齊戴口罩去，都係防武漢SARS。入到去可以同外國團隊叫口號，唱榮光歸香港，去美食檔前面唱十八。同整新春文宣揮春，帶文宣俾外國表演者同旅客知道香港的情況，令香港的人權問題再次受到國際關注，成立國際獨證調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n帶：口罩、食水、乾糧<br />\n不：不消費，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n忌：忌做捉鬼撚<br />\n勇武累了，和理非要走向前，和勇一家，遍地開花<br />\n毋忘初衷，不分化，不篤灰，不割席，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，黎明來到，煲底相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4779a7227c2b2dc22409d90d96c60bac58f4179c","tid":1816464,"uid":125506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"84c313a08c03e3f2c50694bffe9a34f50814a74a","tid":1816464,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"28767ce887b64d1e3abc56d55f1ee214a07b7010","tid":1816464,"uid":258826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245745f41ffe0ddb322db3acf687e86f4bb7f137","tid":1816464,"uid":125506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f926efc18563b56d3ca4936e0ed9a8b88289108a","tid":1816464,"uid":125506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5dd989c0d4e2f931561dcacfc83ec418add7e15e","tid":1816464,"uid":255094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"89ad3ee54c4a1f2e6b40e372ed155fa4bfd4e276","tid":1816464,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score